body_html:
@damiand I have uploaded the training data to a Github repository which can be used as a mirror until the old website comes back up or a TensorFlow official announces a new location.

The temporary mirror can be found (with hash file checksums) here:
https://github.com/Foorack/tensorflow-trainingdata
(yes I know I spelled 'upload' wrong in the initial commit...)

Kind Regards,
~Foorack

@damiand I have uploaded the training data to a Github repository which can be used as a mirror until the old website comes back up or a TensorFlow official announces a new location.

The **temporary** mirror can be found (with hash file checksums) here:
https://github.com/Foorack/tensorflow-trainingdata
(yes I know I spelled 'upload' wrong in the initial commit...)

Kind Regards,
~Foorack
